		<title>First Superman Comic Auctioned</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/superherolegacy/~3/cduo5DO-q8A/</link>
		<comments>http://superherolegacy.com/news/first-superman-comic-auctioned/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Fri, 02 Dec 2011 03:37:10 +0000</pubDate>
